name: Getinmore
overview: Getinmore online training alliance is a trading platform which offers online training and coordinates resources. Cooperating with professional trainers and training institutes from around the world, we are promoting their training resources to the customers around the world, enabling the learners all over the world to get in touch with more professional training and services. We provide cooperation and trading mode like EBAY, but due to the particularity of products, we provide an online training vehicle for products, making trans-regional institutes and members interact with each other by virtue of video, audio, interactive demonstration, group discussion etc (experiencing interaction and contacting our online support). Meanwhile, we also provide extra service, namely the service about marketing promotion.
